name: TC_03_02_03 | Verify navigation to Home page from fromHeader
description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromHeader.
descriptionHtml: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromHeader.

testStage.description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromHeader.

steps.name: Preconditions: Login as a registered user
Click on the "Registered Domains" button in Hearder.
Verify user is redirected to Home page
Verify that Home page has "Millions of domains with the ultimate privacy protection" heading.
